1
00:00:00,653 --> 00:00:03,414
Sherman, film numer dray.

2
00:00:04,450 --> 00:00:09,489
in azelkhe umshtendn, vos hobn geredt tate mame?

3
00:00:10,407 --> 00:00:12,814
ven m'hot alts farbotn?

4
00:00:14,963 --> 00:00:20,677
vo- vo- hot nisht gekent redn, m'hot geredt in di gantse, ikh veys, in shul, vi shlekht un

5
00:00:20,953 --> 00:00:23,481
s'geven tsores.

6
00:00:23,481 --> 00:00:25,368
m'hot nisht gehat gornisht vos tsu zogn.

7
00:00:24,514 --> 00:00:28,018
un s'iz nisht oysgekumen avektsuforn?

8
00:00:27,973 --> 00:00:28,844
NO.

9
00:00:29,172 --> 00:00:30,904
m'hot nisht gehat keyn,

10
00:00:31,551 --> 00:00:34,366
keyn firer zol zogn tsu di yunge,

11
00:00:34,366 --> 00:00:38,430
di tate mames, di zeydes, zey hobn zikh nor gezorgt far di kinder.

12
00:00:38,554 --> 00:00:42,592
un fun di yungvarg hot men nisht gehat

13
00:00:42,592 --> 00:00:45,416
a LEADER vi m'zogt zol zogn

14
00:00:45,439 --> 00:00:47,998
kumts in a vald, kumts do- vayl

15
00:00:48,105 --> 00:00:51,527
m'hot nisht gezen az m'ken zikh shlogn, ven Doytshland iz arayn

16
00:00:51,527 --> 00:00:53,797
azo makht, azoy shtark,

17
00:00:53,797 --> 00:00:57,160
m'hot nisht gegloybt az zey ebn farshpiln a krig meyn.

18
00:00:57,808 --> 00:01:01,683
un m'iz tsugevoynt in a kleyn shtetl tsu zayn barn tate un mame,

19
00:01:01,740 --> 00:01:05,294
un di m'hot zikh nisht gevolt az m'ken lebn in a vald oykhet,

20
00:01:07,056 --> 00:01:08,872
nisht geven vu tsu loyfn,

21
00:01:09,233 --> 00:01:14,250
zenen arayngekumen hobn zey bald oyfgemakht azelkhe plakatn,

22
00:01:14,250 --> 00:01:16,697
oyb eyner bahalt a yid vert er geshosn,

23
00:01:16,697 --> 00:01:20,077
oyb eyner tut dos vert er geshosn, afiles di goyim.

24
00:01:20,218 --> 00:01:23,131
nu hobn di goyim oykhet moyre gehat

25
00:01:23,155 --> 00:01:26,439
ober s'geven a sakh oykhet fun zey vos hobn gemasert,

26
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:29,429
vos az der doytsh hot nisht derkent keyn yid

27
00:01:29,429 --> 00:01:33,729
hobn zey getsaygt, do voynt a yid, do voynt a yid, do voynt a yid,

28
00:01:34,292 --> 00:01:35,889
s'geven azelkhe oykhet.

29
00:01:36,064 --> 00:01:39,922
un vos iz geshen dervayl mit ayer krom, mit ayer gesheft?

30
00:01:40,705 --> 00:01:41,419
ye.

31
00:01:41,419 --> 00:01:48,022
mit di gesheftn hobn zey gemakht az zey hobn tsugemakht di gesheftn, zey hobn gezogt m'tor nisht farkoyfn gornisht,

32
00:01:48,096 --> 00:01:50,109
ales farshraybn vos m'hot,

33
00:01:50,109 --> 00:01:51,583
un gebn zey di list.

34
00:01:52,062 --> 00:01:59,109
un az zey hobn gevolt farkoyfn far an arbetorer epes, far di prayz, far dem gelt vos s'hot gekost far di krig,

35
00:02:00,010 --> 00:02:03,769
hot men es gemuzt gebn far dem vos s'gornisht vert geven shoyn, un

36
00:02:03,769 --> 00:02:05,178
nor vos m'hot getun,

37
00:02:05,178 --> 00:02:06,939
eyder m'hot zey gegebn di list,

38
00:02:06,979 --> 00:02:09,791
hot men bahaltn bay orntlekhe polyakn,

39
00:02:09,814 --> 00:02:15,950
in di tsayt fun a noyt, ze'mir geganen aroysnemen farkoyfn a shtikl skhoyre, mir zoln hobn tsum esn.

40
00:02:16,328 --> 00:02:18,999
a sakh mol m'iz gegangen tsu azan polyak hot er gezogt,

41
00:02:18,999 --> 00:02:21,316
er hot nisht, m'hot gornisht gekent tun.

42
00:02:21,542 --> 00:02:28,826
un a sakh iz geven orntlekhe, zey hobn tsurikgegebn, m'hot farkoyft di shtikl vare, m'hot zey gekoyft broyt, kartofl, farn vinter,

43
00:02:29,068 --> 00:02:32,690
un azoy hot men gelebt vokh bay vokh.

44
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:39,772
un tsu fil esn iz nisht geven shoyn oykhet azoy,

45
00:02:39,772 --> 00:02:43,051
BUT vayl Shmerlev hot gehat a sakh di poyern derlebn

46
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:47,793
hot men zikh a bisl an eytse gegebn, m'iz geganen aroys fun di shtot vos m'hot nisht getort.

47
00:02:48,019 --> 00:02:49,686
un vem m'khapt shist men.

48
00:02:49,686 --> 00:02:51,337
m'hot gemuzt rizikirn.

49
00:02:51,512 --> 00:02:52,805
hot men gemuzt.

50
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:55,066
vi alt zent ir geven in dem moment?

51
00:02:55,545 --> 00:02:58,053
oykhet fertsn, fuftsn yor azoy.

52
00:02:58,212 --> 00:03:01,446
m'iz gega- m'iz aroysgegangen, m'hot gemuzt rizikirn dos lebn.

53
00:03:01,452 --> 00:03:03,203
s'nisht geven rizikirn

54
00:03:03,203 --> 00:03:05,372
dos BUT dos lebn.

55
00:03:05,372 --> 00:03:06,171
ye.

56
00:03:07,982 --> 00:03:10,524
in Shvilov iz geven geto?

57
00:03:10,902 --> 00:03:13,781
der geto iz geven bloyz a SIGN,

58
00:03:14,057 --> 00:03:21,749
dort bald bay der tume, biz danet meg men geyn, vayter tor men nisht, un in di andere ek oykhet azoy, dos iz geven.

59
00:03:21,749 --> 00:03:25,829
m'hot nokh gevoynt oysgemisht mit di polyakn in Shmerle- biz m'hot undz avekgeshikt.

60
00:03:25,937 --> 00:03:26,943
in gantsn.

61
00:03:27,270 --> 00:03:31,331
un vi azoy iz geven voynen dortn un nisht kenen aroysgeyn?

62
00:03:31,978 --> 00:03:34,807
m'hot zikh tsugevoynt, m'gevoynt zikh tsu tsu di tsores.

63
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,620
m'hot zikh tsugevoynt. m'iz gegangen davenen,

64
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:43,382
un m'hot polyakn gekumen tsu undz, m'hot bahaltn vares, un m'hot farkoyft vos m'hot gehat,

65
00:03:43,382 --> 00:03:48,088
a mol a goldn zeygerl, a gold, far esn, ales far esn.

66
00:03:48,145 --> 00:03:49,297
gornisht UNK.

67
00:03:49,297 --> 00:03:51,463
un ontsutun hot men gezen m'zol hobn.

68
00:03:51,351 --> 00:03:57,977
un ayer shtub iz geblibn in dem rayon vos zey hobn ongevizn?

69
00:03:58,725 --> 00:04:01,807
NO, vos heyst ongevizn?

70
00:04:01,476 --> 00:04:02,837
ayer shtub,

71
00:04:02,438 --> 00:04:03,478
nu,

72
00:04:02,978 --> 00:04:05,742
in Shmerlov, iz geblibn in der teyl

73
00:04:05,742 --> 00:04:07,697
vu yidn hobn gemuzt voynen?

74
00:04:07,365 --> 00:04:10,281
NO m'hot nisht dort opgeteylt yidn fun goyim.

75
00:04:10,281 --> 00:04:12,303
biz m'hot undz in gantsn avekgeshikt.

76
00:04:12,951 --> 00:04:17,653
s'geblibn azoy, mit ve- biz m'hot undz avekgeshikt, in eyns in tsvey un fertsik.

77
00:04:17,946 --> 00:04:18,733
ye.

78
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:21,467
dertseylt mir dem moment.

79
00:04:21,928 --> 00:04:22,749
?

80
00:04:22,485 --> 00:04:23,981
dertseylt mir.

81
00:04:24,088 --> 00:04:25,364
vi s'geven?

82
00:04:26,788 --> 00:04:28,064
zikh opruen a bisl.

83
00:04:48,253 --> 00:04:51,347
un un s- s'gevorn azoy.

84
00:04:51,347 --> 00:04:52,731
m'hot shoyn ongehoybn

85
00:04:52,731 --> 00:04:55,419
oystsugefinen fun geto, fun Varshe,

86
00:04:55,628 --> 00:04:56,820
vos tut zikh.

87
00:04:57,298 --> 00:05:02,658
un oykhet m'hot gevust az di doytshn lozn iber

88
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:05,544
yunge boyes tsu der arbet.

89
00:05:06,293 --> 00:05:10,584
hot men gemeynt dos iz shoyn ibergelozt tsum le- dervayl tsum lebn.

90
00:05:10,584 --> 00:05:14,859
un m'hot gevu- m'hot shoyn gehert az yeder tog in nayntsn tsvey un fertsik

91
00:05:14,882 --> 00:05:17,343
hobn zey gemakht JUDENREIN.

92
00:05:17,343 --> 00:05:19,618
heyst es, opgereynikt di yidn in Poyln.

93
00:05:19,641 --> 00:05:22,520
yede tog hobn zey a tsveyte shtot

94
00:05:22,915 --> 00:05:25,086
aroysgeshikt nokh Treblinke.

95
00:05:25,378 --> 00:05:27,903
Treblinke. fun undz iz gegangen Treblinke.

96
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:32,479
hot men zikh yeder tate mame tsugegreyt far zeyere kinder,

97
00:05:32,479 --> 00:05:36,813
zenen geven azoy tsu di kinder, zey hobn zikh nisht gezorgt far zikh ontsugreytn.

98
00:05:36,853 --> 00:05:40,897
nor far di kinder zoln hobn a vikhtiker arbet vos iz vikhtik far di doytshn.

99
00:05:41,089 --> 00:05:44,576
m'zol blaybn lebn. hob ikh genumen, ikh hob gekrign arbet,

100
00:05:44,768 --> 00:05:49,183
a kompanye s'hot geheysn Shimonki, vos m'hot oysgearbet ayzn.

101
00:05:49,695 --> 00:05:52,704
un zekhtsik boyes iz geven dort.

102
00:05:52,704 --> 00:05:56,855
ikh hob gekrign aza pasport vi m'zogt arbets-kart, mit a STAMP az ikh arbet.

103
00:05:56,855 --> 00:05:59,673
az zey hobn a mol gekhapt yinglekh avektsushikn,

104
00:05:59,673 --> 00:06:01,125
ikh hob zey dos getsaygt

105
00:06:01,125 --> 00:06:04,286
hobn zey onerkent dos az ikh hob a plats.

106
00:06:04,393 --> 00:06:06,834
den iz geven zekhtsik

107
00:06:07,633 --> 00:06:11,958
yinglekh kompanye Rudi, dort vu mayn bruder hot gearbet oykhet.

108
00:06:11,958 --> 00:06:14,068
oykhet gehat mit azo dos.

109
00:06:14,068 --> 00:06:18,936
un in di fabrik fun portselan hobn zikh oysgestaret zoln men zey oykhet lozn

110
00:06:18,936 --> 00:06:22,258
a bisl meydlekh un a bisl yinglekh, zekhtsik oykhet.

111
00:06:22,838 --> 00:06:23,659
shoyn.

112
00:06:23,682 --> 00:06:29,953
un m'hot dos gehat. un y- yede tog hot men gehert di nayes, di shtot, di shtot,

113
00:06:30,043 --> 00:06:33,592
un oyb eyner iz gekumen fartseyln rikhtike shlekhte nayes,

114
00:06:33,592 --> 00:06:37,091
iz geven a sakh yidn m'hot nisht gegloybt, m'hot gemeynt der mentsh iz meshuge.

115
00:06:37,401 --> 00:06:39,099
m'hot zikh nisht gelozt tsugloybn.

116
00:06:39,409 --> 00:06:41,715
undz hobn gezogt

117
00:06:42,092 --> 00:06:43,380
iberzetsung.

118
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:46,153
az zi- zi- iberzidlung zi-

119
00:06:46,986 --> 00:06:52,408
VISHEDLENYE az m'zetst, az m'shikt undz arayn oyf a tsveyt plats, beser s'zol zayn.

120
00:06:52,408 --> 00:06:56,345
un m'hot gevolt gloybn dos, m'hot gegloybt in dem az s'vor.

121
00:06:57,432 --> 00:07:03,039
iz in shoyn, yede shtot. eyn mol in nayntsn oktober fuftsn

122
00:07:03,039 --> 00:07:04,681
iz es geven, a tog frier,

123
00:07:04,688 --> 00:07:09,221
ikh hob gehat kompanye, iz gekumen eyner undzers a boy fun Shmelev,

124
00:07:09,295 --> 00:07:10,976
un er hot undz gezogt

125
00:07:11,050 --> 00:07:12,962
az tsu morgns

126
00:07:12,962 --> 00:07:14,250
geyt men undz shoyn.

127
00:07:15,083 --> 00:07:15,752
geyn.

128
00:07:17,108 --> 00:07:18,536
ze'mir aheymgegangen,

129
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:23,818
un m'hot shoyn gezen di yidn fun dem ander shtetl haltn zey in mark,

130
00:07:24,617 --> 00:07:28,428
un zey hobn gezogt zeks in der fri vet men darfn aroysgeyn in der mark arayn.

131
00:07:28,428 --> 00:07:30,366
m'zol zikh nemen zakhn mittsunemen.

132
00:07:31,502 --> 00:07:34,266
s'hot oysgekukt vi s'hot gezen Shindler's List.

133
00:07:34,266 --> 00:07:35,360
di zelbe zakh.

134
00:07:35,451 --> 00:07:40,389
zey hobn geklapt in di fentster zeks in der fri, RAUS! RAUS! RAUS! RAU- poylishe POLICE un zey,

135
00:07:40,446 --> 00:07:43,157
un oyb eyner iz nisht aroysgegangen hot men geshosn.

136
00:07:43,568 --> 00:07:44,321
bald.

137
00:07:44,935 --> 00:07:46,096
un m'iz gegangen,

138
00:07:46,096 --> 00:07:48,253
m'iz geven in mark azoy tsuzamen,

139
00:07:48,411 --> 00:07:49,485
nakher,

140
00:07:49,609 --> 00:07:51,909
hobn di doytshn UNK geredt,

141
00:07:51,909 --> 00:07:54,564
un m'iz geganen tsu aroysrufn fun di listes.

142
00:07:54,756 --> 00:07:56,066
oyf tsu der arbet.

143
00:07:56,680 --> 00:08:01,131
un m'hot, mayn shvester hot gezorgt oyf der list, di mame hot batsolt far ir,

144
00:08:01,131 --> 00:08:06,343
m'hot zi nisht aroysgenumen, ikh veys nisht far vos, efsher a tsveyter, a raykher, hot epes gegebn mer, ikh veys nisht.

145
00:08:06,636 --> 00:08:09,245
m'hot zi nisht gerufn. mikh hobn zey aroysgerufn.

146
00:08:09,707 --> 00:08:11,844
mayn's a shokhnt, Avromele,

147
00:08:12,002 --> 00:08:13,261
hot men gerufn,

148
00:08:13,538 --> 00:08:16,434
ober er hot gezen di froy blaybt, iz er tsurikgegangen.

149
00:08:18,297 --> 00:08:21,820
un dem bruder hot men oykh gerufn, un nakher hot men undz opmarsherirt,

150
00:08:21,820 --> 00:08:23,015
di zekhtsik,

151
00:08:23,224 --> 00:08:24,467
tsu der arbet.

152
00:08:24,625 --> 00:08:26,526
un ikh hob zikh forgeshtelt

153
00:08:27,072 --> 00:08:30,857
az ikh vel tsurikgeyn aheym bay der nakht, ikh hob nisht ge- forgeshtelt

154
00:08:30,857 --> 00:08:31,891
THIS IS IT.

155
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:39,181
SO hot men marsherirt keyn Bozere, finef kilome- dort hot men avekgegangen tsu forn tsu der arbet.

156
00:08:40,065 --> 00:08:41,561
un,

157
00:08:41,922 --> 00:08:44,601
un ven m'iz gegangen gevart oyf di ban dort,

158
00:08:44,601 --> 00:08:49,036
hot men gezen di gantse ban mit shmelever yidn forn keyn Treblinke shoyn.

159
00:08:49,212 --> 00:08:51,875
hot men geshrign GOODBYE! m'hot geveynt,

160
00:08:51,875 --> 00:08:53,576
hot men geshosn tsu undz.

161
00:08:54,325 --> 00:08:56,158
un dos iz geven dos letste mol.

162
00:09:01,615 --> 00:09:03,130
den bay der arbet.

163
00:09:03,130 --> 00:09:05,239
ye, un geyendik dort ahin,

164
00:09:05,239 --> 00:09:08,274
iz geven eyner, er heyst Kon, er voynt in CANADA,

165
00:09:08,989 --> 00:09:10,859
er iz nisht aroysgegangen in mark arayn,

166
00:09:10,859 --> 00:09:13,466
hot undz gezen marsherirn, iz er gegebn a kum tsu.

167
00:09:13,466 --> 00:09:14,217
hot gemeynt,

168
00:09:14,217 --> 00:09:16,070
m'hot gemeynt, iz er gegangen mit undz.

169
00:09:16,110 --> 00:09:18,551
un er iz gegangen mit undz oyf der GRI- SHEBYONKI.

170
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:23,144
un m'kumt aroys, bay der nakht, kumen dray Verkshos, hobn zey geheysn, ukrainer.

171
00:09:23,144 --> 00:09:25,321
un doytshe soldatn mit di biksn.

172
00:09:25,321 --> 00:09:29,176
zey redn tsu undz sheyn, zogn zey, azoy vi m'hot gezen zey kumen geyen tseyln,

173
00:09:29,176 --> 00:09:31,117
iz eyner fun undz gegebn a gey in vald arayn.

174
00:09:31,117 --> 00:09:33,379
soldatn BECAUSE zey veysn zekhtsik.

175
00:09:33,379 --> 00:09:36,019
fre- un vos zent ir tsu do? zogt men zekhtsik.

176
00:09:36,019 --> 00:09:38,176
zogn zey, ober enk ibertsutseyln?

177
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:41,029
mit tsu zikh tsu ibertsaygn ken men? SURE!

178
00:09:41,052 --> 00:09:44,826
eyner zikh avekgezetst, m'hot gehat a tsimerl azoy vi groys vi do, a kekh,

179
00:09:44,882 --> 00:09:47,829
un dray, eyns tsvey dray, tsu shlofn ale zekhtsik.

180
00:09:48,409 --> 00:09:51,457
hot zikh eyner avekgezetst dort vu m'iz geshlofn, mit di biks azoy,

181
00:09:51,835 --> 00:09:55,105
un eyner hot getseylt. geshlogn alts, eyns,

182
00:09:55,105 --> 00:09:56,149
tsvey,

183
00:09:56,290 --> 00:09:58,089
dray, azoy hobn zey undz getseylt.

184
00:09:58,230 --> 00:09:59,940
nokh dem shlogn azoy,

185
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:04,535
zogn zey, vos ets hot, gold zilber, ale dos,

186
00:10:04,609 --> 00:10:05,818
m'zol zey gebn.

187
00:10:06,988 --> 00:10:08,585
un zey hobn ongehoybn tsu zukhn.

188
00:10:09,537 --> 00:10:12,039
un azoy lang gedoyert gedoyert gedoyert,

189
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:14,846
un der man vos iz antlofn in vald arayn bahaltn,

190
00:10:15,274 --> 00:10:18,542
hot gezen s'vert shoyn fintster, zey geyn nisht, iz er gegebn a kum arayn,

191
00:10:18,767 --> 00:10:20,431
o! zogn zey, vos tut er do?

192
00:10:21,062 --> 00:10:25,477
hot men ongehoybn tsu dreyen, zogt men, hot er gezogt zekhtsik, un eyner a forman.

193
00:10:25,905 --> 00:10:30,371
iz eyn un zekhtsik. zogn zey, no, m'hot undz nisht gezogt az eyn un, undz hot men gezogt fun zekhtsik.

194
00:10:30,698 --> 00:10:33,563
un zey hobn im ongehoybn tsu shlogn un tsu shlogn,

195
00:10:33,563 --> 00:10:36,086
un zey hobn ongehoybn zikh tsu soydn, di di ukrainer,

196
00:10:36,086 --> 00:10:39,191
zey hobn aroysgenumen in droysn, m'hot gemeynt zey veln shoyn shisn.

197
00:10:39,191 --> 00:10:42,777
tsurikgekumen mit a tsebrokhene hant, farblutikt, zey hobn gelozt.

198
00:10:42,777 --> 00:10:44,141
ALRIGHT zey hobn gelozt lebn.

